1				! no. of distinct bond
1.0 1				! bond length, no. of similar bonds
Ce ce -3.0 -3.0 -3.0		! ith ion, jth ion, anisotropy (Jxx, Jyy, Jzz)

Note:	line 2 and 3 will be repeat for different bond length.
	Example~
		d1 1
		A B -3.0 -3.0 -3.0
		d2 4
		A B -2.0 -2.0 -3.0
		B C -1.0 -3.0 -1.0
		C D -5.0 -4.0 -4.0
		D E -1.0 -2.0 -3.0
		d3 2
		A E -3.2 -3.1 -3.5
		E C -1.0 -3.0 -2.0
		.
		.
		.
		dn m
		.
		.
		.
		to m, and so on..
